Package: wCCS
Type: Package
Title: Prioritizing Micro-RNA Targets.
Version: 0.3.5
Date: 2012-07-27
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0), GSEABase, pheatmap
Suggests: PGSEA
Author: Iain J Gallagher
Maintainer: Iain J Gallagher <iaingallagher@gmail.com>
Description: This package uses data from the TargetScan database (www.targetscan.org) to prioritise the predicted targeting of genes by a cohort of regulated miRNA. For each mRNA/miRNA interaction listed the TargetScan database provides a context score indicating the confidence in any particular interaction. Using information about miRNA abundance from e.g. a microarray or qPCR survey the wCCS package prioritises the mRNA targets of all selected miRNAs.
License: GPL-3
LazyLoad: yes

